For the single bonds:
- Typical length: 1.53 Å
- Force constant: 500 N/m
- Change in length: \( \Delta x_{\text{single}} = |1.397 - 1.53| = 0.133 \, \text{Å} = 1.33 \times 10^{-11} \, \text{m} \)
