S \approx (1.0545718 \times 10^{-34}) \times 0.8660254 \approx 9.13286 \times 10^{-35}  \mathrm{J \cdot s}.
\]

Expressed in units of \(10^{-35}  \mathrm{J \cdot s}\), this is approximately 9.13286. Rounding to three significant figures, the value is 9.13.

